4Geeks Academy offers a course titled "Become an AI Machine Learning Engineer" that prepares individuals for a career in data science and machine learning. The course is designed for beginners with no prior knowledge in the field. Students will learn Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, and Statistics to become professional data analysts. They will also gain experience creating predictive models using powerful libraries like Pandas and Numpy. The course covers algorithms such as Close Neighbors and Decision Trees, and explores supervised and unsupervised learning models. Students will have the opportunity to solve real-life cases and tackle industry challenges. The duration of the course is 16 weeks, with three classes held each week. The class size is limited to a maximum of 12 people. Upon completion, students will receive a certificate recognized by multiple organizations. There are no specific prerequisites for this course, and students can choose between English and Spanish for the syllabus and content. The course website is [here](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop